    "body": "Problem:\r\nWhen `pum_above` is set, the info window uses `anchor=SW`. Updating the info window height during `CompleteChanged` causes its top edge to shift, so it no longer aligns with the top of the pum.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nUse `NW` as the anchor even when `pum_above` is true so the info window remains aligned with `pum_row`.\r\n\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-12T09:48:15Z",
